statements.sql: select * from `users` where `id` = 35 and `users`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1
select column_name as `column_name` from information_schema.columns where table_schema = 'restaurant' and table_name = 'roles'

select `roles`.*, `model_has_roles`.`model_id` as `pivot_model_id`, `model_has_roles`.`role_id` as `pivot_role_id`, `model_has_roles`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` from `roles` inner join `model_has_roles` on `roles`.`id` = `model_has_roles`.`role_id` where `model_has_roles`.`model_id` = 35 and `model_has_roles`.`model_type` = 'App\User'
select * from `companies` where `companies`.`user_id` = 35 and `companies`.`user_id` is not null and `companies`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1
select count(*) as aggregate from `orders` where `created_at` > '2022-06-24 23:48:52' and `orders`.`deleted_at` is null and `restorant_id` = 17

select ROUND(SUM(order_price+delivery_price),2) as order_price, SUM(delivery_price + static_fee + fee_value) AS total_fee, SUM(delivery_price) AS total_delivery, SUM(static_fee) AS total_static_fee, SUM(fee_value) AS total_fee_value from `orders` where `created_at` > '2022-06-24 23:48:52' and `payment_status` = 'paid' and `orders`.`deleted_at` is null and `restorant_id` = 17 limit 1

select `status`.*, `order_has_status`.`order_id` as `pivot_order_id`, `order_has_status`.`status_id` as `pivot_status_id`, `order_has_status`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id`, `order_has_status`.`created_at` as `pivot_created_at`, `order_has_status`.`comment` as `pivot_comment` from `status` inner join `order_has_status` on `status`.`id` = `order_has_status`.`status_id` where `order_has_status`.`order_id` is null order by `order_has_status`.`id` desc limit 1
select count(*) as aggregate from `status` inner join `order_has_status` on `status`.`id` = `order_has_status`.`status_id` where `order_has_status`.`order_id` is null and `status_id` = 5

select `status`.*, `order_has_status`.`order_id` as `pivot_order_id`, `order_has_status`.`status_id` as `pivot_status_id`, `order_has_status`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id`, `order_has_status`.`created_at` as `pivot_created_at`, `order_has_status`.`comment` as `pivot_comment` from `status` inner join `order_has_status` on `status`.`id` = `order_has_status`.`status_id` where `order_has_status`.`order_id` is null order by `order_has_status`.`id` desc limit 1
select * from `configs` where `model_type` = 'App\Order' and `model_id` is null
select * from `tables` where `tables`.`id` is null and `tables`.`id` is not null

select count(id) as totalPerMonth, ROUND(SUM(order_price + delivery_price),2) AS sumValue, MONTH(created_at) month from `orders` where `created_at` > '2022-01-01 00:00:00' and `payment_status` = 'paid' and `orders`.`deleted_at` is null and `restorant_id` = 17 group by YEAR(created_at), MONTH(created_at) order by YEAR(created_at), MONTH(created_at) asc

select `status`.*, `order_has_status`.`order_id` as `pivot_order_id`, `order_has_status`.`status_id` as `pivot_status_id`, `order_has_status`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id`, `order_has_status`.`created_at` as `pivot_created_at`, `order_has_status`.`comment` as `pivot_comment` from `status` inner join `order_has_status` on `status`.`id` = `order_has_status`.`status_id` where `order_has_status`.`order_id` is null order by `order_has_status`.`id` desc limit 1
select count(*) as aggregate from `status` inner join `order_has_status` on `status`.`id` = `order_has_status`.`status_id` where `order_has_status`.`order_id` is null and `status_id` = 5

select `status`.*, `order_has_status`.`order_id` as `pivot_order_id`, `order_has_status`.`status_id` as `pivot_status_id`, `order_has_status`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id`, `order_has_status`.`created_at` as `pivot_created_at`, `order_has_status`.`comment` as `pivot_comment` from `status` inner join `order_has_status` on `status`.`id` = `order_has_status`.`status_id` where `order_has_status`.`order_id` is null order by `order_has_status`.`id` desc limit 1

select * from `tables` where `tables`.`id` is null and `tables`.`id` is not null
select sum(`amount`) as aggregate from `expenses` where (`created_at` > '2022-06-24 23:48:52') and `expenses`.`deleted_at` is null and `restaurant_id` = 17

select SUM(amount) AS costValue, MONTH(date) month from `expenses` where `created_at` > '2022-01-01 00:00:00' and `expenses`.`deleted_at` is null and `restaurant_id` = 17 group by YEAR(date), MONTH(date) order by YEAR(date), MONTH(date) asc

select `id`, `expenses_category_id`, SUM(amount) AS amount from `expenses` where (`created_at` > '2022-06-24 23:48:52') and `expenses`.`deleted_at` is null and `restaurant_id` = 17 group by `expenses_category_id`

select `id`, `expenses_vendor_id`, SUM(amount) AS amount from `expenses` where (`created_at` > '2022-06-24 23:48:52') and `expenses`.`deleted_at` is null and `restaurant_id` = 17 group by `expenses_vendor_id`

select * from `categories` where `categories`.`restorant_id` = 17 and `categories`.`restorant_id` is not null and (`categories`.`active` = 1) and `categories`.`deleted_at` is null order by `order_index` asc
